description: Submission of reserved matters for Blocks A and M of Phase 2. The proposal comprises 417 residential units and 541 sq m GEA commercial floorspace. A full description of the uses is provided within the Planning Statement / Design & Access Statement submitted with the application. The outline planning application was an environmental impact assessment application and an environmental statement was submitted to the planning authority at that time.
